### ======================================================
### DAILY TASK CONTROLLER
### ======================================================

### 53. Create New Daily Task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "taskTitle": "Fix login issue",
  "taskStatus": false,
  "appName": "Test Application",
  "visitPlace": "Office",
  "assignedTo": "user",
  "assignedBy": "admin",
  "coOperator": "manager",
  "expectedCompletionDate": "2026-04-20T17:00:00",
  "taskPriority": "HIGH",
  "taskNote": "Need to investigate the authentication flow",
  "isRemote": false
}

### 54. Get All Daily Tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 55. Get Daily Task by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 56. Update Daily Task by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "taskTitle": "Updated task title",
  "taskStatus": true,
  "appName": "Updated Application",
  "visitPlace": "Remote",
  "assignedTo": "user",
  "assignedBy": "admin",
  "coOperator": "manager",
  "expectedCompletionDate": "2026-04-25T17:00:00",
  "taskPriority": "MEDIUM",
  "taskNote": "Task completed successfully",
  "isRemote": true
}

### 57. Delete Daily Task by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 58. Get Tasks Assigned To User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/assigned-to/user
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 59. Get Tasks Assigned By User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/assigned-by/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 60. Get Tasks By App Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/app/Test%20Application
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 61. Get Tasks By Status (false=pending, true=completed)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/status/false
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 62. Get Tasks By Priority
GET http://localhost:8080/api/daily-tasks/priority/HIGH
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ======================================================
### ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
### ======================================================
# {
#   "adminToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9...",
#   "managerToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9...",
