### ======================================================
### ERROR RESPONSES
### ======================================================
# Success (200): {"message": "..."}
# Not Found (404): {"error": "User not found with id: X"}
# Bad Request (400): {"error": "Error: Username is already taken!"}
# Unauthorized (401): {"error": "Invalid username or password"}
